"This webform is <a href=\":href\">archived</a>. Only submission "
"administrators are allowed to access this webform and create new "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Šis webforms ir <a href=\":href\">arhivēts</a>. Piekļūt šim "
"webformam un veidot jaunus iesniegumus drīkst tikai iesniegumu "
