"href=\":href\">Problēma #2836374</a>)"

msgid ""
"Examples of elements with <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/RobinHerbots/jquery.inputmask\">input "
"masks</a>."
msgstr ""
"Piemēri elementiem ar <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/RobinHerbots/jquery.inputmask\">ievades "
